								<a href="https://www.thenation.com/issue/june-1-2015/">June 1, 2015 Issue</a>
							</li></ul><h1 class="article_title hide">The Trials of Hannah Arendt</h1><h1 class="title">The Trials of Hannah Arendt</h1><h2 class='subtitle'>Many have delighted in judging Hannah Arendt, maybe because they have feared her judgment.</h2>		
		
		<div class="byline">
			<h2 class="author_name">By <a class="author" href="https://www.thenation.com/authors/corey-robin/">Corey Robin</a></h2>	
					<h4 class="time is_date article_pub_time">
						May 12, 2015											
					</h4>
					</div>
		
		<!--<ul class="article-share">
